Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,{OP}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:00.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,{ED}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.68,0:00:08.69,haven't smelled tatami mats,Sign 0003,0004,0001,0022,,{\an8}{\fad(1364,2726)}I haven't smelled tatami mats in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.02,0:00:05.90,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't smelled tatami mats in a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.88,0:00:17.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Where am I?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.05,0:00:24.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What happened last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.21,0:00:27.95,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Do you remember nothing at all \Nfrom when you were transformed?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.51,0:00:30.05,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.43,0:00:33.46,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But your right hand's still there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.86,0:00:34.95,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Right hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.33,0:00:58.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It's been so long...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.46,0:00:59.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,...since I slept under a roof.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.07,0:01:03.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.86,0:01:04.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.47,0:01:04.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.24,0:01:07.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.84,0:01:09.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.04,0:01:10.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'm taking the call.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.44,0:01:11.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do it right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.25,0:01:11.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Right this second!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.96,0:01:12.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Which button am I supposed to push?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.67,0:01:12.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.90,0:01:15.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,This one? C'mon, hurry up.\NGosh, which one is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.00,0:01:16.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hello?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.84,0:01:18.55,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.80,0:01:21.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.64,0:01:23.79,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Today's another fine day.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.79,0:01:26.02,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How's the new dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.33,0:01:27.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Great, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.71,0:01:31.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Compared to sleeping outdoors, it's heavenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.08,0:01:32.39,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's good to hear.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.98,0:01:37.02,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The change of clothes at your pillow \Nis a gift from everyone at the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.12,0:01:40.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.54,0:01:42.29,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Atsushi-kun,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.29,0:01:44.25,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize for asking \Nthis out of the blue...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.79,0:01:47.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but there's been an emergency.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.66,0:01:48.91,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,An emergency?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.12,0:01:52.01,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, there can be no delay.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.01,0:01:54.19,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Please come to the specified \Nlocation immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.44,0:01:56.00,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It's a crisis!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.00,0:01:57.74,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Only you can help.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.87,0:02:00.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.68,0:03:33.68,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Are you ready, Atsushi-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.09,0:03:34.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.70,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,First, when you leave the room, \Nmake sure you close the door.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.70,0:03:40.15,Stray Dogs - Italics,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Look behind you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.47,0:03:41.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Behind me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.91,0:03:49.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.92,0:03:51.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What's this about?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.81,0:03:53.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.23,0:03:55.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe I'm hallucinating this morning?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.92,0:03:57.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.40,0:03:59.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Is it an enemy attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.16,0:04:01.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get caught in a trap?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.12,0:04:03.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I got in myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.02,0:04:05.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.47,0:04:09.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that there's a way to commit \Nsuicide by getting stuck in an oil drum,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:17.98,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0411,0442,0001,0040,,{\an8}Diagram
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.60,0:04:17.98,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0414,0001,0438,0039,,{\an8}Securing the feet is the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:11.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,so I decided to give it a shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.97,0:04:14.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But now that I have,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.40,0:04:17.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just suffering without \Nbeing able to actually die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.16,0:04:20.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Not to mention, now that I've \Nwedged myself this deep,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.19,0:04:21.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't get out on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.85,0:04:23.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I think I might die.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.30,0:04:24.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.62,0:04:26.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But it's a way to commit suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:29.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,so you should be able to kill yourself \Nif you stay that way, I think?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.32,0:04:32.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I like suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.15,0:04:34.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but I {\i1}don't{\i0} like suffering or pain!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.79,0:04:35.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why would I?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:37.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Also, I only learned this after the fact,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.80,0:04:39.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but it wasn't a suicide method...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.53,0:04:41.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It was a torture method!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:40.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,There.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.56,0:04:44.84,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,My name is Nakajima Atsushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.74,0:04:48.75,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Just the other day,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.17,0:04:54.52,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I turned into a tiger and went on a blind rampage\N and this man, Dazai-san, helped me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.86,0:05:09.18,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,While Dazai-san is this kind of person,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.27,0:05:10.78,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,those people with supernatural powers
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.30,0:05:13.73,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,all belonged to the Armed Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.97,0:05:15.28,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Nakajima Atsushi!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.90,0:05:20.04,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll become one of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.59,0:05:25.16,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,From this day forth, you'll be a \Nmember of the Armed Detective Agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.86,0:05:28.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That was painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.88,0:05:31.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I owe you one, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.13,0:05:36.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Without you, I would've \Nsnapped in two at the waist.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.47,0:05:40.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you ask your other coworkers for help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.77,0:05:42.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I called them, sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.51,0:05:44.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I told them I was on death's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.70,0:05:49.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But then everyone was all \Nlike, "Congratulations."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.47,0:05:50.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,How's that make you feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.78,0:05:52.13,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.91,0:05:55.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.70,0:06:00.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Anyone gifted with supernatural powers \Nhas something wrong with them inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.75,0:06:03.16,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Gifted, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.24,0:06:06.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.49,0:06:12.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone at the Armed Detective Agency... \Nthe private investigators, that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.62,0:06:15.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,They're gifted, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.33,0:06:17.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Right, they're an armed force
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.38,0:06:20.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,taking on antagonists the police \Ndon't stand a chance against.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:23.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't stand a chance at\Njoining the agency, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.74,0:06:26.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're gifted just fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.84,0:06:30.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that I have the supernatural \Nability to turn into a tiger,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.58,0:06:34.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,but I have absolutely no control over it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:38.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I just transform unaware.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.80,0:06:41.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't will myself to \Ntransform into a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.32,0:06:45.74,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So I don't think I'll be \Nof any use, even if I join.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.33,0:06:49.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I really appreciate the offer, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.63,0:06:50.71,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.33,0:06:53.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What's your plan, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.56,0:06:57.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I think I'll look for a job \NI can actually handle,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.83,0:07:00.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,though I don't think it'll be easy to find.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.52,0:07:04.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I have an idea for a potential job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.06,0:07:08.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can help you get it, if you'd like.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.60,0:07:09.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.07,0:07:13.07,Stray Dogs Ep Title,Sign 0711,0460,0001,0048,,A Certain Bomb
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.07,0:07:12.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.40,0:07:18.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to meet the guarantor \Nwho'll introduce you to the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.24,0:07:21.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.05,0:07:23.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What's the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:25.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,No point spoiling the fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.13,0:07:28.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, there may be a test of sorts.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.05,0:07:28.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.68,0:07:29.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A test?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.81,0:07:31.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun, can you write?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.14,0:07:34.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I do know how to read and write.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.62,0:07:36.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Then you'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.17,0:07:39.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be just fine, I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.64,0:07:42.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I guarantee it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:43.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.04,0:07:46.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You'd better thank me!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.48,0:07:49.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Just leave it to me, \Nand everything will be fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.06,0:07:51.90,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,After all, I {\i1}am{\i0} Dazai...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.38,0:07:55.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,The one and only whom the agency trusts
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.14,0:07:57.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and the populace adores!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.83,0:07:59.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Dazai!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.33,0:08:02.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You bandage-squandering machine!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:09.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nice nickname there, Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:17.85,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0806,0004,0001,0035,,{\an8}Bandage-Squandering Machine?!\NThat stung, just a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.54,0:08:17.85,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 0807,0002,0001,0094,,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.17,0:08:12.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the one and only one \Nthe agency trusts, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.97,0:08:14.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one and only one
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.54,0:08:17.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,who we get complaints,\N curses, and grievances about!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.01,0:08:17.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.85,0:08:22.23,Typewriter Text Sign,SIgn 0819,0002,0001,0043,,{\an8}Calls about complaints, curses... \Nand grievances?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.78,0:08:20.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Since when did I ever get a complaint?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.23,0:08:30.69,ideal,Sign 0823,0034,0001,0109,,Ideal
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.03,0:08:25.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Call in August:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.38,0:08:29.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"One of your employees has been \Ncaught in an offshore fishing net."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.39,0:08:30.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Can you come retrieve him?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.37,0:08:33.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Call in September:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.82,0:08:36.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Some weirdo's got himself \Nburied on my farm."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.28,0:08:38.00,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Could he be one of yours?"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.73,0:08:41.19,Stray Dogs - Top,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Th-Th-Th-Th...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.23,0:08:41.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Call in the same month:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.37,0:08:44.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Pay your tab, okay?!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.28,0:08:46.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"All six months' worth!"
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.01,0:08:47.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's impossible...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.64,0:08:51.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Who knew you were so good at imitating \Nother people, Kunikida-kun?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.30,0:08:53.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.04,0:08:57.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Stop ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.97,0:08:59.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's actually a good idea
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:01.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,to have him help me find a job...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.30,0:09:02.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.52,0:09:07.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I wasted a whole minute \Ndealing with this idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.09,0:09:09.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Let's hurry to the agency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.86,0:09:10.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.87,0:09:12.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We have an emergency!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.34,0:09:15.78,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,A bomber's taken a hostage and \Nholed himself up in our office.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.91,0:09:18.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A bomber?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.12,0:09:22.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.87,0:09:23.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.12,0:09:26.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The agency's on the fourth floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.43,0:09:28.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I wanted to ask.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.28,0:09:31.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's take the stairs, just in case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.18,0:09:32.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.93,0:09:34.18,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.43,0:09:35.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.40,0:09:38.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.31,0:09:39.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.69,0:09:40.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I can't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.73,0:09:43.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I can't take it anymore...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.55,0:09:46.67,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,It's all your fault...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.78,0:09:48.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,The Armed Detective Agency's fault.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.91,0:09:51.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.36,0:09:54.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Bring the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.20,0:09:57.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I'll blow everyone to kingdom come.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A personal grudge?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.57,0:10:02.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's inconvenient.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:03.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.74,0:10:05.94,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.39,0:10:09.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,The bomber seems pretty \Nfurious at the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:13.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think I'll be of \Nany use. May I go now?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.41,0:10:16.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We do attract a lot of ill will.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.74,0:10:18.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You're ignoring me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.32,0:10:21.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, that's a high explosive.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.86,0:10:24.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If the bomber acts on his \Nthreat and detonates it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.34,0:10:26.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,the whole floor's as good as gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.55,0:10:27.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh no...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.96,0:10:30.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to mitigate the \Nforce of the explosion somewhat
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.36,0:10:33.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,if we can find something to cover the bomb,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.56,0:10:35.11,safety first,Sign 1034,0001,0014,0083,,{\an8}Safety First
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.43,0:10:37.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but given the circumstances...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.56,0:10:40.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe he took a woman \Nas a hostage, the coward.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.06,0:10:42.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Who's the girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.74,0:10:45.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,She's Naomi-chan, a part-time \Noffice assistant.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.96,0:10:46.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A part-timer?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.59,0:10:50.69,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Then she's a completely innocent bystander!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.47,0:10:52.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.12,0:10:55.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't we let him see the president?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.52,0:10:57.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,He'll try to kill the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.84,0:11:00.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,We can't let the president walk \Ninto a situation like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.02,0:11:02.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad he's out on a business trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.29,0:11:06.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Then there's only one method...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.99,0:11:09.87,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Are they going to use their abilities?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:20.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Go, go.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.11,0:11:21.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,C'mon, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.70,0:11:22.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.60,0:11:25.19,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.19,0:11:26.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.08,0:11:27.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I only want to see the president!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.91,0:11:30.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,If you do anything funny, I'll blow this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.15,0:11:32.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.50,0:11:35.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I know who you are. You're Kunikida!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.88,0:11:38.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I bet you're trying to \Nmake me let my guard down
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.46,0:11:40.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,and use that annoying ability of yours!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.77,0:11:42.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Well, fat chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.08,0:11:45.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Get up on the desk on all fours
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.23,0:11:46.79,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,and keep both hands where I can see them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.89,0:11:51.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I-If you don't do as I say,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.10,0:11:52.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking you all down with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.81,0:12:00.20,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,This isn't good.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.62,0:12:02.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Because of his personal grudge against the agency,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.13,0:12:06.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,he's done his research on all \Nthe members' names and faces.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.79,0:12:11.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If I go, it'll only provoke him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.49,0:12:14.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm... What to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.64,0:12:19.36,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I just got a {\i0}really{\i1} bad feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.07,0:12:23.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,A-tsu-shi-ku—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.31,0:12:23.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.55,0:12:25.12,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't even said anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.27,0:12:27.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I already know what you're going to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.54,0:12:29.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.82,0:12:33.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You're the only one here who's not a formal \Nmember and who the bomber won't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.49,0:12:38.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But even if I were to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.66,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't be able to do anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.76,0:12:41.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.84,0:12:46.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We just need you to distract \Nhim for a short while.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.79,0:12:48.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We'll do the rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.14,0:12:50.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.67,0:12:55.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing you, how about you \Nput on an off-putting act
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.08,0:12:57.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,as a worthless human being?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.51,0:12:59.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Here are some props.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.85,0:13:04.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.96,0:13:07.76,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Scuffles on this scale
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.76,0:13:13.01,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,are child's play to the Armed \NDetective Agency, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:17.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,{eyecatch}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.01,0:13:21.43,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.27,0:13:25.61,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What could you possibly accomplish?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.61,0:13:28.32,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I... I bet this would make your parents sad!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.32,0:13:29.73,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.54,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1330,0446,0001,0043,,{\an8}S-S-S-S-S-S-S-S-S-S-S...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.83,0:13:32.54,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1333,0001,0446,0043,,{\an8}Scary
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.73,0:13:32.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.78,0:13:35.62,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,You're not with the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.28,0:13:38.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,A-A-As you can tell,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.37,0:13:40.41,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm just a newspaper delivery boy\N who happened to pass by!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.58,0:13:42.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,And what's a delivery boy \Ngot to do with any of this?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.45,0:13:45.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how much you might hate them,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.26,0:13:48.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,you shouldn't take hostages or blow up bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.30,0:13:50.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure there's something to live for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.86,0:13:51.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.88,0:13:52.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.85,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1356,0446,0001,0043,,{\an8}Wait a minute...\NDid you just start that thought \Nwithout thinking it through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.89,0:13:57.85,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1357,0444,0001,0045,,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.48,0:13:54.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,What's something to live for?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.32,0:13:57.85,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,T...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.07,0:13:58.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.65,0:14:04.15,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1403,0446,0001,0042,,{\an8}S... S... Sure, that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.77,0:14:01.92,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,T... T... Tea on rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.35,0:14:04.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You can eat a {\i1}lot{\i0} of tea on rice!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.72,0:14:06.52,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You can sleep somewhere \Nwith a roof over your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.06,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,When you go to sleep at night, \Nyou can wake up to a new day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.06,0:14:10.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,And every day is a new day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.57,0:14:12.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.07,0:14:17.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,If you blow up, neither you \Nnor I will see another new day...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.47,0:14:20.16,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,because we'll be dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.35,0:14:21.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I know that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.53,0:14:22.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.80,0:14:25.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.45,0:14:28.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I think you should reconsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.46,0:14:30.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, if you die...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.83,0:14:32.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You're really dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.74,0:14:36.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you might wish \Nyou were dead sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.28,0:14:38.77,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,but there are people who keep on \Nliving, even if the going's tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.77,0:14:40.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, people like me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.17,0:14:43.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I have no family and no friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.59,0:14:45.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I even got chased out of an orphanage,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.65,0:14:46.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and I have nowhere to go,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.86,0:14:48.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and no hope for the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.27,0:14:51.03,Stray Dogs - Italics,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, I even turn into a tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.26,0:14:53.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, that's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.31,0:14:55.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,It's true that, like you say,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.57,0:14:56.93,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I lack redeeming qualities,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.93,0:14:59.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and everyone'd agree that \NI'm the scum of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.24,0:15:02.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But I still manage keep on living \Nwithout going all postal about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.91,0:15:04.63,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Good job, Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:08.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You have acting like a worthless \Nhuman being down to an art form.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.38,0:15:10.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So why don't you toss that bomb aside,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.05,0:15:12.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,and we can look for jobs together?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.33,0:15:13.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.03,0:15:15.99,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1356,0446,0001,0043,,{\an8}You already forgot you're pretending\N to deliver newspapers?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.13,0:15:16.80,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, I'm not exactly looking for one...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.02,0:15:18.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Now, Kunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.21,0:15:19.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.53,0:15:20.47,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Ability:
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.60,0:15:23.52,No Longer Human,Sign 1522,0010,0001,0014,,{\an8}{\fad(695,1)}Doppo Poet
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.11,0:15:22.44,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Doppo Poet...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.05,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Wire Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.57,0:15:26.44,sign_31821_418_Wire_Gun,Sign 1526,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,307)}Wire Gun
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:32.37,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.86,0:15:36.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Get him, Kunikida-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.07,0:15:38.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Like I already said, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.41,0:15:42.09,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,One down!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.09,0:15:44.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Good job, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.94,0:15:52.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"One down," you say?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.44,0:15:57.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"Now!"? "Secure him!"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.29,0:15:59.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You're all talk and no action!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.45,0:16:01.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What choice was there?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.36,0:16:05.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You lost at rock-paper-scissors, \NKunikida-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.05,0:16:07.29,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.29,0:16:10.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, all's well that ends well, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.38,0:16:12.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I've heard that if you're too neurotic,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.00,0:16:15.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,you'll get a lot of wrinkles
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.33,0:16:18.72,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,and your aging becomes accelerated.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.29,0:16:20.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Is that true?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.87,0:16:22.28,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Go on, take notes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.67,0:16:26.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,"If you're too neurotic...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.91,0:16:30.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,...your aging becomes accelerated—"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.31,0:16:30.17,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I'm messing with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.28,0:16:33.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.33,0:16:35.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Stop ridiculing me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.01,0:16:38.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,All of you...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.34,0:16:40.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.22,0:16:41.22,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,Stop making fun of me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.86,0:16:47.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,I swear, anyone gifted with supernatural powers \Nhas something wrong with them inside...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.56,0:16:53.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Thirty seconds left until detonation?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.23,0:16:53.81,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.81,0:16:54.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Bomber,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.95,0:16:56.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Kunikida-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.76,0:16:57.86,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.68,0:17:03.12,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We may be able to mitigate the \Nforce of the explosion somewhat
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.12,0:17:04.41,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,if we can find something \Nto cover the bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.55,0:17:05.91,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Something to cover the bomb...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.04,0:17:07.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Something...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.11,0:17:09.49,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Anything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.16,0:17:16.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Atsushi-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.88,0:17:17.55,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.57,0:17:20.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.65,0:17:22.26,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What am I doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.26,0:17:22.89,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Idiot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.39,0:17:24.07,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.36,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Jeez...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.18,0:17:45.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,I figured he was stupid, \Nbut I didn't know how stupid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.36,0:17:49.68,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,He has the talent to become a suicide maniac.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.68,0:17:52.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Wouldn't you agree, Tanizaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.71,0:17:54.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.02,0:17:54.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.32,0:17:58.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:00.38,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Aw, brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.38,0:18:03.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Are you all right?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.13,0:18:04.13,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.14,0:18:17.28,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1805,0452,0001,0029,,{\an8}Tanizaki Junichirou \NAbility: Light Snow
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.12,0:18:08.82,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,You were so wonderful as a villain!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.28,0:18:17.28,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1808,0001,0446,0029,,{\an8}His Younger Sister \NTanizaki Naomi
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.82,0:18:13.33,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,I had the time of my life \Nbeing tied up and threatened!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:17.27,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Please continue where we \Nleft off, once we get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.97,0:18:21.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So the part-time person was \Nin cahoots with everyone, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:24.65,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Brat, you should blame Dazai.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.01,0:18:29.58,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Barring that, blame yourself for choosing \Nthe wrong person to help you find a job!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.98,0:18:32.04,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Then is this the job...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.21,0:18:35.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,I told you there was a test involved.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.50,0:18:38.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,As in, an entrance exam?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.62,0:18:39.95,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.26,0:18:43.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,The exam has been completed \Nwithout much ado, president.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:44.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.29,0:18:47.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.71,0:18:54.50,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Since Dazai said there \Nwas a capable young man,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.61,0:18:58.32,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1854,0454,0001,0011,,{\an8}President of the \NArmed Detective Agency
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.71,0:18:58.32,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 1856,0001,0442,0012,,{\an8}Fukuzawa Yukichi \NAbility: All Men \NAre Created Equal
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.82,0:18:58.21,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,I had him test your mettle.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.56,0:19:03.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I recommended you for hire,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.96,0:19:07.25,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,but since you've been designated \Na major threat by the ward,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.41,0:19:10.88,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,there was disagreement among us as \Nto whether we should take you in.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.37,0:19:13.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,But Dazai said...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.26,0:19:16.29,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,President.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.47,0:19:22.53,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Suppose the most gifted person \Nin the world appeared before you,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.53,0:19:23.65,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,would you hire him?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:27.30,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Power doesn't make you \Na member of the agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.40,0:19:31.86,Stray Dogs - Flashback,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I recommend him.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.54,0:19:36.48,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,So, president... What is your decision?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.95,0:19:45.70,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let Dazai decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.84,0:19:47.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You can trust me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.35,0:19:50.03,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait a minute, Dazai-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.34,0:19:53.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,So the job you meant to \Nintroduce me for was...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.58,0:19:55.24,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You apparently passed the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.72,0:19:59.34,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to the Armed Detective \NAgency, Nakajima Atsushi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.07,0:20:02.10,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.22,0:20:04.57,Stray Dogs - Default,Tani,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.57,0:20:05.59,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, please, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.01,0:20:09.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,I can't possibly join a workplace \Nas violent and reckless as this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.96,0:20:14.98,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Not just anyone would use their body \Nto shield a bomb to save everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.98,0:20:18.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. I was really impressed!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.57,0:20:20.23,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.92,0:20:22.14,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.87,0:20:36.42,Typewriter Text Sign,Sign 2028,0442,0001,0026,,{\an8}Secretary \NHaruno Kirako
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.12,0:20:31.54,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,So, president, do you actually \Nwant him to join the agency, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.96,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a tea leaf's standing straight up...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.31,0:20:41.87,Stray Dogs - Default,Haruno,0000,0000,0000,,I think something good \Nwill happen, president.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.43,0:20:47.42,Stray Dogs - Default,Fuku,0000,0000,0000,,Ouch.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.32,0:20:50.31,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Still, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.33,0:20:54.02,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,If you still refuse, we can't force you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:59.45,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,But then, I can't help but \Nworry for your future.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.63,0:21:03.53,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,We'll need you to vacate the company dorm...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.53,0:21:06.08,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,You don't really have any specialized skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.08,0:21:09.51,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,nor do you have friends or know anyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.51,0:21:11.46,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,That'd make finding a job very difficult.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.66,0:21:15.30,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you are a wanted tiger.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.09,0:21:17.56,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Should anyone learn of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.56,0:21:19.40,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,at best you'd get fired from your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.68,0:21:22.39,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,At worst, you'd be captured and shot dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.39,0:21:23.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Sh-Shot dead?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.13,0:21:26.15,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Now, if you were with this agency...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.54,0:21:28.64,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,it'd be a different story.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.64,0:21:30.75,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Then that means...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.98,0:21:33.84,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,We look forward to working \Nwith you, Atsushi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.91,0:21:35.35,Stray Dogs - Default,Naomi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't we, brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.46,0:21:37.60,Stray Dogs - Default,Kuni,0000,0000,0000,,Follow the rules, brat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.26,0:21:40.11,Stray Dogs - Default,Dazai,0000,0000,0000,,Well, now that's been settled...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.22,0:21:41.99,Stray Dogs - Default,Naka,0000,0000,0000,,You've got to be kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.91,0:23:23.97,Stray Dogs - Default,Higuchi,0000,0000,0000,,The weretiger has been found.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.93,0:23:39.97,Stray Dogs Next ep title,Sign 2337,0380,0001,0126,,Episode 2: Yokohama Gangster Paradise
